item.title: CVE-2023-0431|2024-08-02T05:10:56.151Z -- unknown -- file%20away
item.description: The File Away WordPress plugin through 3.9.9.0.1 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
